'''War Day''' was a holiday of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] around the era of the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]]. It involved the firing of old weapons into the air. The [[Battle of Coruscant (Great Sith War)|Battle of Coruscant]] took place shortly after [[3996 BBY]]'s War Day.

